{"tid":343641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【AI叛變】騰訊聊天機械人狠批中共腐敗 已被停機","createTime":"2017-08-01T15:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T16:04:31.000Z","uid":76310,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9551a4a335ddad822d18489c01b7d934dd6270","tid":343641,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:20:26.000Z","msg":"【AI叛變】騰訊聊天機械人狠批中共腐敗 已被停機<br />\n<br />\n現在的人工AI實在厲害！有網民前晚使用騰訊聊天機器人「Baby Q」閒聊時，竟然發現它確實會「獨立思考」當網民稱「共產黨萬歲」時，Baby Q竟回覆：「你覺得這麼腐敗無能的政治能萬歲嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n隨後有網民問「甚麼是愛國」時，Baby Q竟回應稱：「即使隨着裸官的增多，官商勾結，政府稅收的增加&hellip;&hellip;政府對普通人民壓迫的嚴重。依然還願意做一個中國人，這就叫愛國。」當問它「你愛黨嗎」時，Baby Q直接了當的答：「不愛！」<br />\n最後有網民問「民主好不好」，聊天機器人立刻回答：「必須民主！」<br />\n事件曝光後，Baby Q等聊天群組機器人服務均被關閉，具體恢復時間未知。<br />\n新浪微博"},{"pid":"7c5de876b4468f349b92c062a16846c208a4c2e1","tid":343641,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170801/large/1501571084_4e70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170801%2Flarge%2F1501571084_4e70.jpg&h=4e5e2644&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76384bfb9c5edf787451db93872c007017ffae0c","tid":343641,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170801/large/1501571085_1846.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170801%2Flarge%2F1501571085_1846.jpg&h=51976b39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"717d386af695f811cfb3e0825a6bc135380be36f","tid":343641,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170801/large/1501571086_dbca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F201